================================================================================

GOLDEN REFERENCE OUTPUTS
================================================================================

The files under golden-outputs/*.expected are the verbatim stdout captures
from running each COBOL test program with GnuCOBOL 3.2 on Linux/AMD64.
They are factual representations of program execution and serve only as
test fixtures.

================================================================================

DEPENDENCIES
================================================================================

This repository has zero runtime dependencies beyond OpenJDK 11+. The
validation harness additionally depends on GnuCOBOL 3.2 (installed via
the system package manager inside the Docker image) for the optional
"compile-from-source" verification path.
